ActDepartment of Employment and Social Development Act
PrecisAppointment of LOUISE LEVONIAN of Ottawa, Ontario, Associate Deputy Minister of Employment and Social Development, to be styled Senior Associate Deputy Minister of Employment and Social Development and Chief Operating Officer for Service Canada, to hold office during pleasure; and as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Vice-Chairperson of the Commission, effective July 28, 2014.
